# Project Documentation

This folder contains the complete documentation for the **AI-Enabled Student Admission System**, developed using Salesforce Developer Edition.

## Project Overview

The AI-Enabled Student Admission System is a Salesforce-based intelligent admission management solution designed to automate and improve student admission processing.

The system uses Salesforce automation and AI capabilities to:

- Manage student admission applications
- Evaluate application completeness
- Check academic eligibility
- Track document verification
- Generate AI-powered admission guidance
- Send automated application status notifications
- Capture feedback on AI-generated guidance
- Provide admission reports and dashboards
- Implement role-based access control

## Technologies Used

- Salesforce Developer Edition
- Salesforce Flow Builder
- Agentforce
- Prompt Builder
- Reports & Dashboards
- Validation Rules
- Email Alerts
- Profiles & Permission Sets

